snippet.title: Antioch: Scarlet Bay - Coming 2018 on mobile
snippet.description:
http://antiochgame.com/
https://twitter.com/AntiochGame
https://www.facebook.com/antiochgame/
 
Antioch : Scarlet Bay is a multiplayer interactive fiction, developed by Midnight Mood Studio, written by FibreTigre and published by Mi-Clos Studio.
You’ll play as two detectives working together to solve an intriguing crime.
The adventure will bring you in the city of Antioch, a dark metropole surrounded by moutains and sea.
 
Music by Ville Veistonen
http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/709686
https://soundcloud.com/ville-veistonen
